intent.user_query: What is the percentage of orders fulfilled within 7 days of the order date?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN (ShippedDate - OrderDate) <= 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DECIMAL(10,2)) / COUNT(*) * 100 AS PercentageOrdersFulfilledIn7Days FROM fitness_db.Orders WHERE ShippedDate IS NOT NULL;

arguments.sql: SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN (ShippedDate - OrderDate) <= 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DECIMAL(10,2)) / COUNT(*) * 100 AS PercentageOrdersFulfilledIn7Days FROM fitness_db.Orders WHERE ShippedDate IS NOT NULL;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
